data.description: Lightning fast response! Welcome to an exquisite contemporary-style home in the upgraded portion of Poinciana. On this huge lot, you have ample space to create the home of your dreams. Spanning over 1500 square feet, this home grants you the flexibility and space to design your living space to fit your special style. This newly built home, 2018, will allow you to seamlessly blend simplicity and style to create that one-of-kind living space with peace of mind of being a brand new house.    Prepare to be impressed as you drive into your new attached 3-car garage that will fit your biggest of vehicles. The space is so big, you use the space to fit your hard to store items, or even additional living space/office if your feeling bold enough. But that's not all—step outside to discover your new personalized relaxation haven. This enchanting outdoor space sets the stage for unforgettable family gatherings and summer soirées with the family you love the most. In your fully fenced-in backyard, you can craft your own personal oasis, create cherished memories for your family, or simply unwind and disconnect from the outside world.    Don't let this extraordinary opportunity slip through your fingers! Schedule your private tour today. With a move-in date available by the end of the month, your new beginning awaits!
